This OCR implementation of XSBENCH requires up to 8GB of memory (depending on the problem size - large problem requires 8 GB memory) which is higher than the default memory size specified in the default config files. Hence, appropriate config files have been generated using the scripts provided under ocr/Configs
To build and run

x86:
make -f Makefile.x86 clean run

x86-mpi:
make -f Makefile.x86-mpi clean run
